  "title": "Creative Intern",
  "description": "<p>Creative Internship (Full-time, 6 months)<br /><em>With the opportunity to convert to a permanent role for strong performers.</em></p><p>We’re looking for a Creative Intern who lives on TikTok/Instagram, enjoys coming up with fun ideas, and isn’t afraid of testing, failing, and trying again. You’ll be part of the core content team, not just “helping out”.<br /></p><p><strong>You will:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Brainstorm and research content ideas for TikTok & Instagram based on trends, hooks and what people are actually watching.</p></li><li><p>Help plan and structure content (hooks, flow, CTAs) so videos are clear, engaging and easy to follow.</p></li><li><p>Edit short-form videos using tools like CapCut / Premiere Pro or similar.</p></li><li><p>Create simple, eye-catching social assets (posts, stories, basic graphics) using Canva / Adobe tools.</p></li><li><p>Support on shoots: planning shot lists, preparing props, helping on set and coordinating with creators.</p></li><li><p>Give suggestions on how to improve content based on feedback and basic performance data (views, watch time, saves, etc.).</p></li><li><p>Handle ad-hoc creative and production tasks to keep campaigns moving smoothly.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Nice-to-haves (bonus points):</strong></p><ul><li><p>Comfortable or open to occasionally appearing on camera, or helping direct on-camera talent.</p></li><li><p>Basic understanding of TikTok / IG analytics or interest in performance marketing.</p></li><li><p>Previous personal projects (school work, passion projects, TikTok/IG account, etc.) you can show us.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Who you are:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Active user of TikTok and/or Instagram, up to date on trends and formats.</p></li><li><p>Creative, curious and willing to share ideas, even if they’re not perfect yet.</p></li><li><p>Responsible and organised with deadlines, files and communication.</p></li><li><p>Open to feedback and eager to learn fast in a start-up style environment.</p></li></ul><p><strong>What you’ll get:</strong></p><ul><li><p>6-month full-time internship with structured guidance and real responsibility.</p></li><li><p>Stipend + potential performance bonuses if your content drives strong results.</p></li><li><p>Hands-on experience creating content for real brands.</p></li><li><p>Mentorship from a small, fast-moving team and a chance to convert to a full-time role if there’s a good mutual fit.</p></li></ul>",
